PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of Fisheries and Oceans of Peter D. Allen, of Yellowknife, Northwest Territories, as a director of the Board of Directors of the Freshwater Fish Marketing Corporation to hold office during pleasure for a term of two years, in the place of Calvin Sidney Kirwan, whose term has expired.
